<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>URGENT: Inventory Sync Failure</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 20px;
            background-color: #f4f4f4;
            color: #333;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }
        .container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 20px auto;
            background-color: #ffffff;
            padding: 30px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }
        h1, h2, h3 {
            color: #f0ad4e; /* Orange for warning */
        }
        ul {
            list-style: none;
            padding: 0;
        }
        ul li {
            margin-bottom: 8px;
        }
        strong {
            color: #333;
        }
        pre {
            background-color: #eee;
            padding: 10px;
            border-radius: 5px;
            white-space: pre-wrap;
            word-break: break-all;
        }
        a {
            color: #007bff;
            text-decoration: none;
        }
        a:hover {
            text-decoration: underline;
        }
        .footer {
            margin-top: 30px;
            font-size: 0.9em;
            color: #777;
            text-align: center;
            border-top: 1px solid #eee;
            padding-top: 15px;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <h3>⚠️ URGENT: Inventory Sync Failure for SKU: <%= sku %></h3>
        <p>The system failed to update the inventory for a product on an external platform.</p>
        <ul>
            <li><strong>Product SKU:</strong> <%= sku %></li>
            <li><strong>Product Name:</strong> <%= productName %></li>
            <li><strong>Platform that Failed:</strong> <%= platformName %></li>
            <li><strong>Reason for Failure:</strong>
                <pre><%= errorMessage %></pre>
            </li>
        </ul>
        <p>Please manually review the inventory for this product on <%= platformName %> and in the admin dashboard to prevent overselling.</p>
        <p><a href="https://brandsdiscounts.com/admin/products/sku/<%= sku %>">View Product in Admin</a></p>
        <div class="footer">
            <p>This is an automated alert. Action is required.</p>
            <p>&copy; <%= new Date().getFullYear() %> Brands Discounts. All rights reserved.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
